We have erected
a new theme park

7
00:00:19,416 --> 00:00:21,541
in order to allow the ladies
to further experience

8
00:00:21,625 --> 00:00:24,375
the particulars
of Commoner culture.

9
00:00:24,458 --> 00:00:27,833
It's called... Shominland.

10
00:00:27,916 --> 00:00:29,208
[KIMITO]
Are you for real?

11
00:00:29,291 --> 00:00:31,291
That's where you come in,
Mr. Kagurazaka!

12
00:00:31,375 --> 00:00:32,291
While at Shominland,

13
00:00:32,375 --> 00:00:33,375
we want you to
offer the students

14
00:00:33,458 --> 00:00:35,041
all the guidance
and advice you can.

15
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:36,916
[KIMITO]
You sure that's a good idea?

16
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,416
