34
00:01:08,416 --> 00:01:09,250
[KUJO]
In any case...

35
00:01:09,333 --> 00:01:10,750
The opportunity has now come

36
00:01:10,833 --> 00:01:12,458
for you to put your
Commoner know-how

37
00:01:12,541 --> 00:01:14,083
to its greatest purpose yet.

38
00:01:14,166 --> 00:01:15,916
You must demonstrate your
abilities and knowledge

39
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,375
to their fullest extent.

40
00:01:17,458 --> 00:01:19,458
This is, perhaps,
the most significant moment

41
