in your entire life to date.

42
00:01:21,416 --> 00:01:23,083
[KIMITO]
No pressure though, right?

43
00:02:59,041 --> 00:03:01,375
[REIKO] I am very
anxious and excited.

44
00:03:01,458 --> 00:03:05,166
I cannot wait to see this
Shominland firsthand!

45
00:03:05,250 --> 00:03:06,875
