they're at a frickin' rave.

76
00:04:17,208 --> 00:04:18,583
This place must be awesome.

77
00:04:21,041 --> 00:04:24,208
Or not at all.

78
00:04:24,291 --> 00:04:26,125
I bid you welcome
to Shominland:

79
00:04:26,208 --> 00:04:28,291
A park modeled after
an average city block

80
00:04:28,375 --> 00:04:29,791
in front of a train station.

81
00:04:38,916 --> 00:04:41,875
[STUDENTS chattering]

82
00:04:44,250 --> 00:04:45,250
Keep it together!

83
00:04:45,333 --> 00:04:46,500
Don't quit on me!

84
00:04:46,583 --> 00:04:48,750
We made it this far,
we can't give up now.

85
00:04:48,833 --> 00:04:50,791
Muster what courage you have!

86
