A traffic signal!

87
00:04:55,458 --> 00:04:56,791
[STUDENT 6A]
Look, it's a crosswalk!

88
00:04:56,875 --> 00:04:57,666
[STUDENT 6B]
I've read about these,

89
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,500
