00:05:20,541 --> 00:05:22,958
It is custom to pass out
tissues at train stations.

99
00:05:23,041 --> 00:05:24,708
[KIMITO] That's typically
done one at a time!

100
00:05:24,791 --> 00:05:25,833
[KUJO]
They are silky-soft.

101
00:05:25,916 --> 00:05:27,500
The best tissues money can buy.

102
00:05:27,583 --> 00:05:30,333
