naught but comfort.

105
00:05:33,416 --> 00:05:34,625
[KIMITO]
Hello?!

106
00:05:34,708 --> 00:05:36,125
Now...

107
00:05:36,208 --> 00:05:38,375
Allow me to direct you to
our first attraction, ladies.

108
00:05:40,666 --> 00:05:42,666
[KUJO] This is, by far,
the most popular restaurant

109
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:44,416
amongst the Commoner populace.

110
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:45,916
[CLERKS]
How can I help you today?

111
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,791
[STUDENTS]
Ahh!

112
00:05:47,875 --> 00:05:49,041
At this restaurant.

113
00:05:49,125 --> 00:05:50,958
Before eating, you must
first place your order

114
00:05:51,041 --> 00:05:53,208
at that counter.

115
00:05:53,291 --> 00:05:55,791
[REIKO]
My word! Are you in earnest?

116
00:05:55,875 --> 00:05:58,083
[KUJO] There are detailed
menus on the countertops.

117
00:05:58,166 --> 00:06:00,833
Look them over thoroughly and
give your order to the clerk.

118
00:06:00,916 --> 00:06:02,583
This is certainly unusual.

119
00:06:02,666 --> 00:06:06,083
But after we complete our order,
then we may sit at a table?

120
00:06:06,166 --> 00:06:08,791
No. You must first
wait to collect your food.

121
00:06:08,875 --> 00:06:09,875
[STUDENTS gasp]

122
00:06:09,958 --> 00:06:12,375
Oh my...
Let me make sure I understand.

123
00:06:12,458 --> 00:06:15,250
We order... Then we stand there?

124
00:06:15,333 --> 00:06:16,458
[KUJO]
Yes.

125
00:06:16,541 --> 00:06:18,625
Food preparation can
take quite a long time.

126
00:06:18,708 --> 00:06:20,416
We might be standing
there waiting for our meal

127
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:22,166
for hours and hours on end.

128
00:06:22,250 --> 00:06:24,666
Wait. Why must this be?

129
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:26,125
That's the way it is.

130
00:06:26,208 --> 00:06:29,000
Here, customers must carry
their own food to the table.

131
00:06:29,083 --> 00:06:30,583
It's commoner custom.

132
00:06:32,083 --> 00:06:33,333
[ALL gulp]

133
00:06:33,416 --> 00:06:35,500
Behold! This is self-service.

134
00:06:35,583 --> 00:06:36,708
[STUDENTS gasp]

135
00:06:43,541 --> 00:06:45,791
