how to order.

168
00:07:49,791 --> 00:07:51,500
[KIMITO]
Teriyaki burger combo upsized

169
00:07:51,583 --> 00:07:53,208
with a large cola to drink.

170
00:07:53,291 --> 00:07:54,833
