173
00:08:00,625 --> 00:08:01,458
One more time!

174
00:08:01,541 --> 00:08:03,125
[AIKA]
Teriyaki burger combo!

175
00:08:03,208 --> 00:08:04,833
This is the moment
you've been waiting for,

176
00:08:04,916 --> 00:08:05,916
so seize it.

177
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,208
Walk right up to
that counter and speak!

178
00:08:08,291 --> 00:08:09,833
"Teriyaki burger combo.

179
00:08:09,916 --> 00:08:12,250
Upsized with a large cola
to drink!" Right now!

180
00:08:12,333 --> 00:08:13,833
[AIKA sighs]

181
00:08:13,916 --> 00:08:15,375
[KIMITO]
What are you so worried about?

182
00:08:15,458 --> 00:08:16,041
Go on!

183
00:08:16,125 --> 00:08:17,583
[AIKA whimpering]

184
00:08:17,666 --> 00:08:19,875
[KIMITO] Something tells me
this isn't gonna end well.

185
00:08:23,041 --> 00:08:24,125
Umm...

186
00:08:24,208 --> 00:08:26,166
I'd like to place my
order first, please.

187
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:30,166
[KAE]
Reiko is so amazingly brave!

188
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:31,625
[MAYA]
Good luck up there!

189
00:08:43,666 --> 00:08:44,875
Good afternoon to you.

190
00:08:44,958 --> 00:08:47,041
Will your order be
for here or to go?

191
00:08:48,708 --> 00:08:49,750
[REIKO]
Not here.

192
00:08:49,833 --> 00:08:50,958
If it's all right with you,

193
00:08:51,041 --> 00:08:52,708
I would prefer to eat
over at the tables.

194
00:08:52,791 --> 00:08:54,666
Please allow me
to clarify, Miss Reiko.

195
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:56,041
She is asking whether
you'll be eating

196
00:08:56,125 --> 00:08:57,291
in the dining space here,

197
00:08:57,375 --> 00:08:58,791
or whether you'd like
your meal wrapped up

198
00:08:58,875 --> 00:09:00,166
so you may take it home.

199
00:09:00,250 --> 00:09:01,791
Oh. I see.

200
00:09:01,875 --> 00:09:04,625
I could bring it home for
a tea party, couldn't I?

201
00:09:04,708 --> 00:09:06,708
[STUDENT 6H] Yes, it would
be like having a picnic,

202
00:09:06,791 --> 00:09:07,750
but indoors!

203
00:09:07,833 --> 00:09:09,041
[STUDENT 6I]
That would be lovely!

204
00:09:09,125 --> 00:09:10,458
[CLERK 6B]
What would you like to order?

205
00:09:10,541 --> 00:09:11,791
[REIKO gasps]

