[KIMITO]
It's hopeless.

216
00:09:30,666 --> 00:09:32,125
The teriyaki burger meal.

217
00:09:32,208 --> 00:09:34,458
It's the most popular
combo by far.

218
00:09:34,541 --> 00:09:36,083
Oh, thank you.

219
