but that's a lot of food to eat.

220
00:09:39,125 --> 00:09:41,250
I'd just stick with
the standard upsize.

221
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:42,583
Right.

222
00:09:42,666 --> 00:09:43,875
I would like to order one
teriyaki burger combo

223
00:09:43,958 --> 00:09:45,208
upsized, please.

224
00:09:45,291 --> 00:09:46,750
That'll be right up, Ma'am.

225
00:09:46,833 --> 00:09:49,083
Your meal comes with a drink.
What would you like?

226
00:09:49,166 --> 00:09:51,625
If I were you, I'd try
the new blended tea.

227
00:09:51,708 --> 00:09:53,833
[REIKO] Wonderful,
I'll have the tea, then.

228
00:09:53,916 --> 00:09:55,541
Thank you very much, Ma'am.

229
00:09:55,625 --> 00:09:58,500
Please stand over there to the
side 'til your order is ready.

230
00:09:58,583 --> 00:10:01,375
I do so appreciate
your assistance, Kimito.

231
00:10:01,458 --> 00:10:03,541
[MAYA] He is a gentleman,
through and through.

232
00:10:03,625 --> 00:10:05,666
[KAE]
Always there to lend a hand.

233
00:10:08,958 --> 00:10:10,375
Can I have that?

234
00:10:10,458 --> 00:10:12,208
[CLERK 6B] So, you'd like
a kids' meal then?

235
00:10:12,291 --> 00:10:14,250
No. I don't need the meal.

236
00:10:14,333 --> 00:10:17,416
I, uh... I just want the toy.

237
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:19,250
