238
00:10:20,875 --> 00:10:22,750
[STUDENT 6Y]
This place really is amazing!

239
00:10:24,625 --> 00:10:25,750
[MAYA]
Oh, my!

240
00:10:25,833 --> 00:10:27,833
[STUDENT 6J]
I enjoy just looking at it.

241
00:10:27,916 --> 00:10:30,041
All right. Let us eat.

242
00:10:31,916 --> 00:10:33,708
[KIMITO] Wait a sec,
where did Aika go?

243
00:10:42,791 --> 00:10:44,875
